The '''''Rover''''' was a [[Skiff/Legends|skiff]] assigned to the [[Anakin Solo (starship)|''Anakin Solo'']]. It was led by [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] apprentice [[Ben Skywalker]] to [[Terephon]] in order to find out what became of [[Jaina Solo Fel|Jaina Solo]] and [[Zekk]]. The ship was destroyed when it tried to warn the [[Queen Mother]] of the deception of [[Galney (Ducha of Terephon)|Ducha Galney]]. The crew consisted of Ben Skywalker, [[Chief Petty Officer/Legends|Chief Petty Officer]] [[Tanogo]], [[Junior Lieutenant/Legends|Junior Lieutenant]] [[Beta Ioli]] and gunner [[Gim Sorzo]]; Sorzo and Skywalker went EV with Jaina and Zekk before the ''Rover'' was destroyed.

